casebody.data:
Lequan FOX
v.
STATE of North Carolina No. 72P17-3 Supreme Court of North Carolina. September 21, 2017 Lequan Fox, for Fox, Lequan Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 21st of September 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 21st of September 2017."
